  "detailed_description": "<h1>TINY HOUSE SIMULATOR: EARLY ACCESS ROADMAP</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191990/extras/a628812bcf2285fc2e69718ce0ffa2dd.avif?t=1730921112\" width=616 height=1310 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191990/extras/d977a0bc7df7d48563ef57db0a6fca0b.avif?t=1730921112\" width=616 height=71 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191990/extras/392bda1b75baba9dfd3a7c1cbff06e2f.poster.avif?t=1730921112\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191990/extras/392bda1b75baba9dfd3a7c1cbff06e2f.webm?t=1730921112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Create Tiny Houses for Clients: Design one-of-a-kind and inviting tiny homes on wheels. Personalize each home to reflect your clients' tastes and add your flavor. Whether you're building rustic cabins or modern minimalist structures, the options are endless!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191990/extras/7b29efc629d4e87cd4e072357e7a2561.avif?t=1730921112\" width=616 height=71 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191990/extras/1dd2f6f5e9d2d49d9e0dd1253de79749.poster.avif?t=1730921112\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191990/extras/1dd2f6f5e9d2d49d9e0dd1253de79749.webm?t=1730921112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Set off on a journey across a vibrant, diverse island where every twist reveals a new delight. Check out the bustling town on the west coast, relax by the peaceful central lake, or venture towards the mountainous southeast.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191990/extras/25fbce148ebc882e75f09c4110fee81a.avif?t=1730921112\" width=616 height=71 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191990/extras/9f17644b8bb617b153167e028e663d75.poster.avif?t=1730921112\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191990/extras/9f17644b8bb617b153167e028e663d75.webm?t=1730921112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Take the reins on how you grow your business, design your tiny homes, and explore Tiny Island. The open-world gameplay offers limitless experiences tailored to your unique style.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191990/extras/da2ed398980fbae9599d935dfb461a63.avif?t=1730921112\" width=616 height=71 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191990/extras/cfe902188e749e87a1c3f14eb524e8e9.poster.avif?t=1730921112\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191990/extras/cfe902188e749e87a1c3f14eb524e8e9.webm?t=1730921112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Hook your creations to your trusty vehicle and bring them to satisfied clients around the island. Traverse winding roads, picturesque paths, and challenging terrains to meet your deadlines.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191990/extras/999bad8367f7dc8c849719925990b224.avif?t=1730921112\" width=616 height=71 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191990/extras/9e54439ec1b2a7731a6db528e5f08a56.poster.avif?t=1730921112\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191990/extras/9e54439ec1b2a7731a6db528e5f08a56.webm?t=1730921112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Oversee and grow your tiny house business. Use your hard-earned money to upgrade your workshop, buy a better vehicle, or try your luck in the local casino. Aim to craft even bigger and more captivating homes!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191990/extras/35dde028a0223b67bfa5fb17c21781d4.avif?t=1730921112\" width=616 height=71 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191990/extras/5947fa6356bf2f5f3d13aafcd251776c.poster.avif?t=1730921112\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191990/extras/5947fa6356bf2f5f3d13aafcd251776c.webm?t=1730921112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Enjoy the breathtaking views and attractions, including a fairground, windmills in the hills, and a lighthouse on a tiny isle. Chill out on the sandy shores or explore the buzzing airport in the southwest.<br><br>Are you ready to take on the ultimate tiny house challenge? Start this fulfilling adventure and turn your small-scale dreams into a thriving business!  <br>Get Tiny House Simulator on Steam today and begin building your dream homes!",
